column5: I wont be able to make it.  We have had tickets since this fall for the saturday taping of the Rick Mercer Report (I originally thought it was Dave's Cousin or something...... but were gonnna go anyway...)  We are meeting some old friends and spending the weekend.  Anyway, theres TWO Sportsmans Show entry tickets to the first person who can tell me what the check in time at the Fishing for Tyler event is on Saturday!!  Good luck!!
Largemouths got them... pm me you full mailing info and ill get them out to ya!!
When Maureen gets there to collect our money...  Don't forget to register your kids under sixteen or they won't be eligible to win or have their names in the draw...
